# Aguka Smart Farming Kit - Backend

## Environment Variables

```env
# Server
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000
API_VERSION=v1

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/aguka

# Redis
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-min-32-chars
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your-super-secret-refresh-key-min-32-chars
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=15m
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# Firebase
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=aguka-smart-farming
FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=firebase-adminsdk@aguka.iam.gserviceaccount.com
FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY=-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n

# Africa's Talking (SMS/USSD)
AFRICASTALKING_USERNAME=sandbox
AFRICASTALKING_API_KEY=atsk_eebe9cce6aba0c7fab9d62a9349ded8b57dc195fde03f3916d8425f73ffed79a9a9d3187
AFRICASTALKING_SHORTCODE=*384#

# Twilio (Voice)
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your-twilio-account-sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-twilio-auth-token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+250XXXXXXXXX

# MQTT
MQTT_BROKER_URL=mqtt://localhost:1883
MQTT_USERNAME=mqtt_user
MQTT_PASSWORD=mqtt_password

# Email (Optional)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=agukasmartfarmingkit@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=badz xfqs tkoe jebl

# Frontend URL (CORS)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:5173
```

## Setup

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Generate Prisma client
npm run db:generate

# Run migrations
npm run db:migrate

# Start development server
npm run dev

# Build for production
npm run build

# Start production server
npm start
```

## API Base URL

```
http://localhost:3000/api/v1
```